CREATE
OR REPLACE PROCEDURE "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_CCTRANSACTIONS_SP" () LANGUAGE SQLSCRIPT SQL SECURITY INVOKER AS BEGIN DECLARE batch_size INTEGER := 2000;

DECLARE offset INTEGER := 0;

DECLARE total_records INTEGER;

DELETE FROM
    "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_CC_TRANSACTIONS"
WHERE
    recordID IN (
        SELECT
            A.recordID
        FROM
            "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_CC_TRANSACTIONS" A
            INNER JOIN "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_OBJ_CREDITCARD_TRANSACTIONS" B ON A.recordID = B.ID
        WHERE
            A.EVENTTIME <= B.EVENTTIME
            AND B.PROCESSED_FLAG IS NULL
            OR B.EVENTTYPE = 'delete'
    );

UPDATE
    "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_OBJ_CREDITCARD_TRANSACTIONS"
SET
    PROCESSED_FLAG = 'Y'
WHERE
    ID IN (
        SELECT
            A.ID
        FROM
            "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_OBJ_CREDITCARD_TRANSACTIONS" A
            INNER JOIN "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_CC_TRANSACTIONS" B ON B.recordID = A.ID
        WHERE
            A.EVENTTIME < B.EVENTTIME
            AND A.PROCESSED_FLAG IS NULL
            AND A.EVENTTYPE <> 'delete'
    );

CREATE LOCAL TEMPORARY TABLE "#INTERMEDIATE_RESULTS" AS (
    SELECT
        T1.*,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY T1.ID
            ORDER BY
                T1.EVENTTIME DESC
        ) AS rn
    FROM
        "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_OBJ_CREDITCARD_TRANSACTIONS" AS T1
    WHERE
        T1.PROCESSED_FLAG IS NULL
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT
                1
            FROM
                "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_OBJ_CREDITCARD_TRANSACTIONS" AS T2
            WHERE
                T2.EVENTTYPE = 'delete'
                AND T1.ID = T2.ID
        )
);

DELETE FROM
    "#INTERMEDIATE_RESULTS"
WHERE
    rn > 1;

SELECT
    COUNT(*) INTO total_records
FROM
    "#INTERMEDIATE_RESULTS";

WHILE offset <= total_records DO
CREATE LOCAL TEMPORARY TABLE "#JSONDATA" (JSON CLOB);

INSERT INTO
    "#JSONDATA" (JSON)
SELECT
    JSON
FROM
    "#INTERMEDIATE_RESULTS"
LIMIT
    :batch_size OFFSET :offset;

INSERT INTO
    "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_CC_TRANSACTIONS" (
        recordEventType,
        eventTime,
        recordID,
        transactionId,
        ccTaccountId,
        ccTlastSegment,
        paymentType,
        lastModified,
        ccTprocessType,
        transactionStatus,
        merchantCity,
        merchantCountry,
        merchantState,
        merchantStreetAddress,
        merchantPostalCode,
        merchantCategorycode,
        merchantId,
        merchantName,
        merchantStandardcategorycode,
        merchantReferencenumber,
        postedAmountcurrency,
        postedAmount,
        postedDate,
        transactionCurrencycode,
        transactionAmount,
        transactionDate,
        transactionType,
        companyId,
        cardProductType,
        addendumType,
        hasRichData,
        integrationPartner,
        isDeletable,
        receiptImageId,
        customerVatNumber,
        description,
        description2,
        description3,
        description4,
        description5,
        doingBusinessAs,
        vatNumber,
        processorReferenceNumber,
        referenceNumber,
        transactionDateTime
    )
Select
    recordEventType,
    eventTime,
    recordID,
    transactionId,
    ccTaccountId,
    ccTlastSegment,
    paymentType,
    lastModified,
    ccTprocessType,
    transactionStatus,
    merchantCity,
    merchantCountry,
    merchantState,
    merchantStreetAddress,
    merchantPostalCode,
    merchantCategorycode,
    merchantId,
    merchantName,
    merchantStandardcategorycode,
    merchantReferencenumber,
    postedAmountcurrency,
    postedAmount,
    postedDate,
    transactionCurrencycode,
    transactionAmount,
    transactionDate,
    transactionType,
    companyId,
    cardProductType,
    addendumType,
    hasRichData,
    integrationPartner,
    isDeletable,
    receiptImageId,
    customerVatNumber,
    description,
    description2,
    description3,
    description4,
    description5,
    doingBusinessAs,
    vatNumber,
    processorReferenceNumber,
    referenceNumber,
    transactionDateTime
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            *
        FROM
            JSON_TABLE(
                "#JSONDATA".JSON,
                '$' COLUMNS (
                    recordEventType VARCHAR (200) PATH '$.type',
                    eventTime TIMESTAMP PATH '$.time',
                    recordID VARCHAR(100) PATH '$.id',
                    NESTED PATH '$.data' COLUMNS (
                        merchantReferencenumber VARCHAR (100) PATH '$.merchantReferenceNumber',
                        transactionDate DATE PATH '$.transactionDate',
                        postedDate TIMESTAMP PATH '$.postedDate',
                        transactionType VARCHAR (10) PATH '$.type',
                        transactionId VARCHAR (100) PATH '$.id',
                        companyId VARCHAR (100) PATH '$.companyId',
                        customerVatNumber VARCHAR (100) PATH '$.customerVatNumber',
                        description VARCHAR (200) PATH '$.description',
                        description2 VARCHAR (200) PATH '$.description2',
                        description3 VARCHAR (200) PATH '$.description3',
                        description4 VARCHAR (200) PATH '$.description4',
                        description5 VARCHAR (200) PATH '$.description5',
                        processorReferenceNumber VARCHAR (100) PATH '$.processorReferenceNumber',
                        referenceNumber VARCHAR (100) PATH '$.referenceNumber',
                        transactionDateTime TIMESTAMP PATH '$.transactionDateTime',
                        NESTED PATH '$.account' COLUMNS (
                            ccTaccountId VARCHAR(50) PATH '$.id',
                            ccTlastSegment VARCHAR(5) PATH '$.lastSegment',
                            cardProductType VARCHAR(10) PATH '$.cardProductType',
                            NESTED PATH '$.paymentType' COLUMNS (
                                paymentType VARCHAR (10) PATH '$.id'
                            )
                        ),
                        NESTED PATH '$.administrativeData' COLUMNS (
                            lastModified TIMESTAMP PATH '$.lastModified',
                            ccTprocessType VARCHAR(10) PATH '$.processType',
                            transactionStatus VARCHAR (10) PATH '$.status',
                            addendumType VARCHAR (10) PATH '$.addendumType',
                            hasRichData VARCHAR(5) PATH '$.hasRichData',
                            integrationPartner VARCHAR (50) PATH '$.integrationPartner',
                            isDeletable VARCHAR(5) PATH '$.isDeletable',
                            receiptImageId VARCHAR (100) PATH '$.receiptImageId'
                        ),
                        NESTED PATH '$.merchant' COLUMNS (
                            merchantCategorycode VARCHAR (10) PATH '$.categoryCode',
                            merchantId VARCHAR (50) PATH '$.id',
                            merchantName VARCHAR(200) PATH '$.name',
                            merchantStandardcategorycode VARCHAR(10) PATH '$.standardCategoryCode',
                            doingBusinessAs VARCHAR (200) PATH '$.doingBusinessAs',
                            vatNumber VARCHAR (100) PATH '$.vatNumber',
                            NESTED PATH '$.address' COLUMNS (
                                merchantCity VARCHAR (50) PATH '$.city',
                                merchantCountry VARCHAR(10) PATH '$.countryCode',
                                merchantState VARCHAR (50) PATH '$.state',
                                merchantStreetAddress VARCHAR (50) PATH '$.streetAddress',
                                merchantPostalCode VARCHAR (10) PATH '$.zip'
                            )
                        ),
                        NESTED PATH '$.postedAmount' COLUMNS (
                            postedAmountcurrency VARCHAR (10) PATH '$.currencyCode',
                            postedAmount FLOAT PATH '$.value'
                        ),
                        NESTED PATH '$.transactionAmount' COLUMNS (
                            transactionCurrencycode VARCHAR (10) PATH '$.currencyCode',
                            transactionAmount FLOAT PATH '$.value'
                        )
                    )
                )
            )
    ) AS c6
WHERE
    transactionId is not null;

DROP TABLE "#JSONDATA";

Commit;

offset := offset + batch_size;

END WHILE;

END;

CREATE LOCAL TEMPORARY TABLE "#INTERMEDIATE_RESULTS" AS (

        FROM
                "SAP_CONTENT#SAP_CONCUR_EXP_DDS"."CONCUR_EXP_DDS_OBJ_EXPENSE_REPORT" AS T1

                AND NOT EXISTS (

                        FROM

                        WHERE
                                T2.EVENTTYPE = 'delete'
                                AND T1.ID = T2.ID
                )
);
